  "short_description": "Snowscape is a roguelite adventure that combines top-down survival with snowmobile racing. Race down risky snowy mountains by day and survive the monstrous horrors lurking in the dark by night. Can you escape the twisted nightmare of this mysterious, frozen wilderness?",
