  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/7a680d35c85cd6055ed08668b1ec3d2e.poster.avif?t=1738615482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/7a680d35c85cd6055ed08668b1ec3d2e.webm?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/7a680d35c85cd6055ed08668b1ec3d2e.mp4?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re an explorer who answered a distress signal on this snowy peak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yet when you arrived, you found nothing—no one in sight. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To make matters worse, your helicopter crash-landed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/80d48662fe81b8977cb7e6911b2145a5.poster.avif?t=1738615482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/80d48662fe81b8977cb7e6911b2145a5.webm?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/80d48662fe81b8977cb7e6911b2145a5.mp4?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don’t freak out, though—you’ve got a small but trusty snowmobile to rely on!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Carve through endless snow trails.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Launch snowballs like a pro to smash through obstacles.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Collect coins to upgrade your ride.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/8ecc563bcc4bb5c0a8d8a646e5e2beb2.poster.avif?t=1738615482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/8ecc563bcc4bb5c0a8d8a646e5e2beb2.webm?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/8ecc563bcc4bb5c0a8d8a646e5e2beb2.mp4?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you try to rest in your tent, you’ll realize the mountain’s nightlife is not your friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defend your camp from the chilling creatures of the snowfields, and find the Eternal Flame to protect your camp.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/b06a666b99262e293df9675288e0d451.poster.avif?t=1738615482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/b06a666b99262e293df9675288e0d451.webm?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/b06a666b99262e293df9675288e0d451.mp4?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may feel alone here, but… something’s watching you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Do not resist the strange, ethereal energy that seeks to help you. It may be your only ally.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/625ecad556e56f02ea8859b6fda60772.poster.avif?t=1738615482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/625ecad556e56f02ea8859b6fda60772.webm?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/625ecad556e56f02ea8859b6fda60772.mp4?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember, a great explorer is always prepared. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gather fuel for your snowmobile and make ready for the next day’s descent.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/8a0016f280334c32b7a4c999701bb88a.poster.avif?t=1738615482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/8a0016f280334c32b7a4c999701bb88a.webm?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/8a0016f280334c32b7a4c999701bb88a.mp4?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run out of gas? Do not lose hope.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You’ve still got the ultimate survival skill: “Snowball Transformation”!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive, race, and explore—are you up for the challenge?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/d3d8a0e53890a514867f11d6f8913a15.poster.avif?t=1738615482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/d3d8a0e53890a514867f11d6f8913a15.webm?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/d3d8a0e53890a514867f11d6f8913a15.mp4?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Snowscape is dropping SOON!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/6b41961a19410594164f9270d80b4d48.poster.avif?t=1738615482\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/6b41961a19410594164f9270d80b4d48.webm?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/6b41961a19410594164f9270d80b4d48.mp4?t=1738615482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
